<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Erhard von Herberstorff</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass der Jude N. Pyman, Bürger zu Nürnberg, alles zurückgegeben hat.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_495" id="247r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_495_r2l17"><expan>Erhart<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>Herberſtorff<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_495_r2l18"><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Erhart / Als Jr vns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt /
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Pyman des Juden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_495_r2l19"><expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / . Den
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir beſant vnd
                            <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> brief <expan>hör<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_495_r2l20">darauf cʒerede geſacʒt vnd er hat vns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / Er hab des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_495_r2l21">
<expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> nichts / vnd was Jr Jm geſecʒt habt / das <del rend="strikethrough">alles </del> hab er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_495_r2l22">ew alles <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . Dewht ew <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> /
                        daʒ Jr <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü Jm iht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_495_r2l23"><expan>cʒeſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> het /
                                <expan>Dar<ex>vmb</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir ew <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>ſcheinbot<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_495_r2l25"><expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt
                                <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒog<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ſlewnig<ex>en</ex></expan> rechtens <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_495_r2l24"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Jm </ab></add>
<expan>helffe<ex>n</ex></expan> vor des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_495_r2l26">Reichs <expan>Richt<ex>er</ex></expan> hie cʒü
                                <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> vvenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_495_r2l27">ſo <expan>d<ex>er</ex>ſelb</expan> Jud
                                <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> anheim ıſt / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>vts<ex>upra</ex></expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_495" id="247r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Erhart<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Herberstorff<ex>er</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Erhart, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Pyman, des juden,
                            <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, den <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        besant und <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> brief <expan>hör<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan> und darauf cze rede gesaczt und er hat uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, er hab des
                            <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> nichts und, was ir im geseczt habt, das
                        hab er ew alles <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Dewht ew <expan>ab<ex>er,</ex></expan> daz ir
                                <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> czü im iht <expan>cze
                                sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> het, <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ew <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheinbot<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt
                            <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>slewnig<ex>en</ex></expan> rechtens <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<add><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> im</add>
<expan>helffe<ex>n</ex></expan> vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> hie czü
                            <expan>Nur<ex>emberg,</ex></expan> wenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den,</expan> so <expan>d<ex>er</ex>selb</expan>
                        jud, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger,</ex></expan> anheim ist. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>ut s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
